<subSubSection pageId="104" pageNumber="704" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="104.[179,1385,720,1147]" pageId="104" pageNumber="704">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[181,532,1035,1069]" pageId="104" pageNumber="704">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. Lorentz’s Mosaic-tailed Rat is widespread, and is present in some protected areas.
</paragraph>
